 * jenkins/Jenkinsfile  — PowerShell implementation (THIS IS THE ACTIVE PIPELINE)
 * jenkins/Jenkinsfile.python — Python implementation (reference / pending)
 *
 * Copy the desired flavour to the repo root and name it 'Jenkinsfile'
 * before handing it to Jenkins, or configure the Jenkins job to load it
 * from the sub-directory directly:
 *
 *   Pipeline definition → Jenkinsfile from SCM → Script Path: jenkins/Jenkinsfile
 *   Pipeline definition → Jenkinsfile from SCM → Script Path: jenkins/Jenkinsfile.python
 *
 * Both files are complete, self-contained pipeline definitions with
 * zero references to the other language.  Pick one and delete the other.
